{"tid":1531612,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"聽講專出魔警既康樂中學聽日有罷課集會","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T04:20:02.000Z","uid":178470,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e51403bc977f592ba57c19e27fb46d3c78244f64","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:31:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認撚住我呀，隻抽呀！</span></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;香蕉糖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察執行職務係唔需要出示委任證</span></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;Wave Sir <br />\n<br />\n仲有一個荃灣舉槍指向記者，用腳<span style=\"color: red;\">推開</span>傳教士既黑警<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全部都係大埔嗰間康樂中學畢業</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有frd話佢哋學生打算聽日舉行罷課集會，各位手足可以的話出去支持下佢地，因為今日佢地罷課都被打壓，唔比帶gear抗議，仲被趕去圖書館入面靜坐<br />\n<br />\n聽日八點！<br />\n大家出黎呀！"},{"pid":"3d362f910d58700e530a21cf2f3dec23a349923b","tid":1531612,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d47fec8b22014ec4e7b4bbe2efd07cdff583053","tid":1531612,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"有冇同學會將師兄既相貼係學校表揚架<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"b34207b27e4e33467382a2e5fda37e8e0395b1b1","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d47fec8b22014ec4e7b4bbe2efd07cdff583053","tid":1531612,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"有冇同學會將師兄既相貼係學校表揚架<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"要啦，人地操場有咁大個牆<br />\n唔係唔善用下呀"},{"pid":"c44481e8053ff35c425589de0898a8d9280845c0","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"f97ddb8e9147aba7a017953172091ae1a5a55301","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"7da5533002747fa7d6df4c0c80fbac223e703e2a","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"01be96ceebbbdb25af468875adb54eef3e777096","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a71239d13cdb11509e0adda231dbe2d0a70f83e7","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:53:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79f386782ae3639ba2b00f20ac6620a44d47c6b3","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b500010657cb74cde5d4be0a643f7745ade8ae09","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"出黎呀<br />\n難得黑警中學仲有清算"},{"pid":"bf9a4d638cbcf694c34d79173ab1b52e882791d9","tid":1531612,"uid":206176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:43:50.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷課不罷學戰術討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530836</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbadf43f7b4cfb597857967100e33b503ab5e6f3","tid":1531612,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s